headline: Assessing IQVIA Holdings (IQV) Valuation After DCRI Collaboration And 2026 Growth Guidance
summary: IQVIA Holdings (IQV) shares are in focus after the company announced a new collaboration with the Duke Clinical Research Institute to support obesity and cardiometabolic trials, alongside recently reported 2025 results and 2026 revenue guidance. See our latest analysis for IQVIA Holdings.
